main event: On October 6, 1965, two unidentified circular objects were reported in the sky near Baker, Oregon.
interesting points: The objects were photographed as part of the UFO report., The report includes 9 photographs, showing various ambiguous images of the night sky., Several images depict bright spots which may be celestial objects., Some images show a cloudy formation of lights without identifiable features., The photographs are described as grainy and lacking clear details.
